description: The MGMT port for the frame link module in bay 2 is unlinked.  It should be linked to the management network because a OneView appliance is present in appliance bay 2.

eventDetails.eventItemValue: Connect the MGMT port from the frame link module to the management network to ensure the most resilient connection to the management network.  Ensure the cable is functioning properly and it is a compatible cable type.  Check the status of the connected network devices. {"name":"Learn More","uri":"/doc#/cic/s_ts-enc-bk-em4"}
